                     <interp inst="t18250113-126-person671" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I took him in charge; he said he took it from distress - he had not a farthing about him. His apparel seemed to bear every mark of poverty.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>The prisoner pleaded urgent distress.</p>
